WEBVTT

00:00.134 --> 00:01.915
Previously on
<i>"Legends of Tomorrow"...</i>

00:01.920 --> 00:04.470
<i>- It's a dragon egg.
- You're possessed.</i>

00:04.535 --> 00:06.351
Ray's gone.
I've taken over his body.

00:06.352 --> 00:07.640
<i>If Neron wanted John dead,</i>

00:07.720 --> 00:09.270
<i>he would have killed
him on the spot.</i>

00:09.350 --> 00:11.060
<i>I need you to open up
a doorway to hell.</i>

00:11.140 --> 00:13.618
<i>It's to bring someone here
from the other side.</i>

00:13.620 --> 00:14.480
<i>Tabitha.</i>

00:14.560 --> 00:17.040
I'm sorry. It wasn't me.
It was my nipple.

00:17.725 --> 00:20.065
Save me!
As you wish.

00:22.531 --> 00:23.445
I'm not leaving Mona behind.

00:23.525 --> 00:25.605
Do you really think
that everyone in hell

00:25.615 --> 00:26.825
deserves to be there?

00:26.826 --> 00:28.775
This is your opportunity
to make things right.

00:28.855 --> 00:30.875
I'm gonna save Ray.

00:31.905 --> 00:33.875
<i>Honey, time to go.</i>

00:35.075 --> 00:38.285
Come on, honey, let's go.
We're gonna be late.

00:38.365 --> 00:41.165
Zari? You better not
be eating the Halva.

00:41.245 --> 00:44.045
No, Mommy.

00:44.055 --> 00:47.045
Zari Jaan.

00:47.125 --> 00:49.725
Dessert's not for
after breakfast.

00:52.225 --> 00:53.885
What?

00:53.965 --> 00:57.185
It's only a kick.

00:59.065 --> 01:01.735
Behrad must be anxious
to meet you.

01:01.815 --> 01:04.405
Now go put your shoes on
so I can take you to school.

01:10.085 --> 01:12.405
<i>You might just want
to soak it all in.</i>

01:12.415 --> 01:15.245
<i>Violent people are pouring
into our country...</i>

01:15.255 --> 01:18.825
<i>Illegal immigrants,
terrorists, meta-humans.</i>

01:18.905 --> 01:20.535
<i>Politicians promise
to keep you safe</i>

01:20.615 --> 01:22.585
<i>but they've been
hiding the truth.</i>

01:22.595 --> 01:26.415
<i>There's a dangerous new threat
already within our borders.</i>

01:26.435 --> 01:28.675
<i>Hi, I'm Ray Palmer.</i>

01:28.745 --> 01:32.095
<i>Yes, that Ray Palmer...
Former CEO of PalmerTech.</i>

01:32.105 --> 01:33.595
<i>And I am here to warn you</i>

01:33.605 --> 01:35.175
<i>that creatures once thought only</i>

01:35.255 --> 01:37.935
<i>in legends and fairy tales
are real.</i>

01:41.015 --> 01:43.475
<i>Yes, folks, monsters are real,</i>

01:43.555 --> 01:44.855
<i>and they walk amongst us.</i>

01:44.935 --> 01:46.605
<i>And they will stop at nothing</i>

01:46.615 --> 01:48.905
<i>until they destroy humankind.</i>

01:48.975 --> 01:50.365
<i>Interested in learning more?</i>

01:50.435 --> 01:53.625
<i>Then join me at PalmerX 2019,</i>

01:53.695 --> 01:57.905
<i>where the power is in
the Palmer of your hands.</i>

02:01.155 --> 02:03.545
I don't care if Neron's
wearing my best friend's face.

02:03.615 --> 02:05.625
I want to punch him.
Get in line.

02:05.635 --> 02:08.125
Ogres are big softies... that
one wouldn't even hurt a fly.

02:08.134 --> 02:10.215
Neron's been a step
ahead of us for too long.

02:10.294 --> 02:12.475
We need to play offense.
Agreed.

02:12.555 --> 02:14.135
Sorry, what are we agreeing to?

02:14.145 --> 02:17.385
Look, it's time for us
to fight back.

02:17.465 --> 02:19.435
We're retaking the Bureau.

02:19.825 --> 02:24.735
<font color="#00FFFF">Synced & corrected by</font> <font color="#D81D1D">MaxPayne</font>
